body:
**Re: Pack** is a modular client-side mod for Minecraft 1.20.1, designed to enhance your experience with toggleable features.

<details>
<summary>Death Module</summary>
Replaces the default death sound with voice lines from _Re:Zero_, and occasionally triggers a special event.

_Most for fun._

1. Enable/disable;
2. “Instant Resurrection” option, which disables the standard “Screen of Death”;
3. Regular “The Witch Whispers” event, which plays a custom sound after death;
4. Rare event “The Witch Calls”, which plays screen effects after death: particles, shaking;
5. Chance setting (default - 1/10) for a rare event, as well as switching the screen effect: particles, shaking.
</details>



<details>
<summary>Guide Module</summary>
Adds a brewing stand tutorial overlay

> Subcategory “Brewing Guide, Part 1”:
1. Enable/disable;
2. Image position (left, right, top, or bottom);
3. Position settings (Y and X coordinates);
4. Image size settings (width and height).

> Subcategory “Brewing Guide, Part 2”:
1. Enable/disable;
2. Image position (left, right, top, or bottom);
3. Position settings (Y and X coordinates);
4. Image size settings (width and height).
</details>

_P.S. You can change the images by creating a resource pack that contains your images at /assets/repack/textures/gui/brewing_guide/_
